Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction flows with the rhythm of the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and causes alibi tricks to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko's world of Karuizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there's trouble with a spicy case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're running late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, old man, it's nothing to get heated up over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Why the heck do I, Kogoro Mouri, have to serve as a driver for two brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're from the Suzuki Financial Group, don't you have your own chauffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't want a chauffer driving me around on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate feeling like I'm being watched!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there's one kid who's got a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so be careful you don't catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took me a while to get Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be okay, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a cold, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, just fine. I just got the sniffles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now that we're all set, off we go to Karuizawa! All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:17.72,Title,,0,0,0,,Suspicious Spicy Curry\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, but If you start feeling bad, tell me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, with that cold, why didn't you just stay home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager at Poirot offered to watch you for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want to go to Karuizawa to see Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s villa too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:51.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And besides, if I know Sonoko for who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}she'll probably think up some no good plan like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We'll do just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll get a really good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? We're going to play tennis to get guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! Around this time, the tennis courts near our villa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are full of college students!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, if you do something like that, Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will get mad at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s the only guy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's going to get someone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll use a tennis outfit to show off your body and wow a guy,{this line is somewhat bluffed because it was not included in utb and the manga phrases it really weird but its my best guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you'll take a photo with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and send it as an e-mail attachment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll do all this to get that boyfriend of yours, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think Shin'ichi will get jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew she was up to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Besides, the only thing I have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a track suit from Teitan High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have tennis wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought you tennis wear and brought it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tada! Super mini, and cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Short!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! I could never wear something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring spats with me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess there's no choice then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll just have to wear your plain panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:22.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}P-Plain panties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit! I'd love to see that, but not if other people see it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't know what you guys are up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if my daughter is embarrassing herself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for that detective brat, I'm turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there will be lots of university babes there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,University babes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so nice in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Where are all my university babes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can't play tennis then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't know if I should feel happy or sad over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, I was looking forward to seeing Ran's panty flash shots that I hadn't seen in a while today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I guess it's for the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Somebody's on the tennis court...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could they be, a university babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:39.63,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiroto Akashi (32)\NTennis Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was just recalling memories of when I first met my wife here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's already taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you guys came to play tennis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would you like me to coach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a tennis instructor, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My house is nearby, so if you're interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer, but I'm afraid we're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, so we couldn't catch any men after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,let's catch some fish instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey, what's with this turn of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I'll catch us some delicious fish for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the villa, the cook and my big sister are waiting with dinner already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't the river water rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, the fish took my bait and tackle off again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you don't tie it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fish lines are smooth, so unless you tie them like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Your rod, it's being pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, I must have hooked a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?! That's my rental car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been washed into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Didn't I tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}you parked the car too close to the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit! I'm not letting the river take the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give up, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but my right wrist hurts a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you sprained it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably landed on it when you fell into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's way better than being stranded in the water!{this line im not sure on since manga/anime give two completely different things}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of our things were in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our cell phones are all out of range,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's getting dark after all of this walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you think we might be lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! You mean you've been walking around not knowing where we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I've just been following my intuition...{another line where anime and manga are different and idk which one is right}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean people are living out in the mountains like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the mountains? It must be a mountain witch!{this line im not sure on}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's have her take us in for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to get a change of clothes for this brat, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sorry to intrude at this hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You guys are the ones who are monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:59.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Iwao Akashi (32)\NHiroto's Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So are you guys more solicitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you brought kids, you can't trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. We're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!\NThis is no place for swindlers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a funny story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys fell into the river while trying to fish out your car that drifted into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. But he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this sling, and a splint to fix his wrist in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll recover in no time. {i think i lost a line here but idk how id fit it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, please turn this way and let me look inside your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your throat is red and your voice is getting hoarse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so try to avoid using your voice too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you might get acute laryngitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I used to be a personal trainer and a coach for a pro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I learned a lot from when I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways, how do the clothes from my childhood fit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they the right size?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They fit perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I smell curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just leftovers from last night though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do you guys want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is delicious! Restaurant quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of your sore throat Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you get eggs over rice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like the spiciness of this curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife must be a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who made this was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife passed away 3 years ago today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why you were at the tennis court recalling memories of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, back when I was a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made healthy meals for my players, focusing on nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was a better cook than my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to go take some curry to my father upstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so help yourselves to seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, I brought you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sure is taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already been 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This long pull string hanging from the light above!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It keeps getting in the way of me eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining! You've already had two plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That string is for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted a string he could reach with his hunched back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you sure took a long time, considering all you did was give him curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my father started saying some strange things, so we started talking to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm not going to eat because I want to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his wife and his daughter-in-law died before him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he thinks that he has a curse placed on him by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he seems to be fine now that he got some curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since it's his favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The road is blocked due to a landslide,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you can't come pick us up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got some spare futons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you go get my father's dish for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, keep in mind, he's a slow eater and can be uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If his light is still on, he's still eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so just come back down quietly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The room's light is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Quietly, quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a stance for a forehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He must be done eating by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back up to get his dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Quietly, quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, the light is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not on his futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's bleeding from his mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still warm, but his toes are starting to stiffen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I estimate that he's been dead for around 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but can you call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the Gunma police officers will be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, the Gunma officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been summoned so here I am, ta-daaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I would go through fire and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain may have blocked the roads, but when you called I came immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does the Gunma Police Station have nobody else to dispatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? What kind of murder case is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the weapon? Any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to do it, right?\NThe Sleeping Kogoro deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop smiling all over the place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have some prudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we're don't even know if this is a murder case yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the body over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is the owner of this house, Iwao Akashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was discovered by
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my daughter Ran, who came to clear his curry dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she found him, the room's light was turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when she checked hour and a half earlier, the light was on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she thought he was still eating his curry and didn't enter the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I checked immediately after the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he seemed to have been dead for about 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were four of us in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we were all in the living room downstairs for at least 2 hours, so we all have alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't in the living room then, because I was taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That means, the one who committed the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would be you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the first time I came to this house was today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where the rope is kept, so I couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a bit concerning that the victim is bleeding from his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since this is obviously a suicide—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What makes it concerning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought people who die like this always bleed from their mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I've seen it all the time in movies and on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor told me once that when something is wrapped around your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your face gets swollen due to the blood circulation stopping, so you don't bleed from the mouth {this line doesnt fit}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unless the inside is cut or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So in movies and on TV, I think they do it to make it visually obvious that the person is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, don't try to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll strain your throat with your cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if it's as the boy said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he's bleeding from his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's due to him going to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he went to go to the dentist about a hurting cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I ask who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Iwao Akashi's son, Hiroto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He adopted me when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His right molar has been pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that after he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it bled from here, causing blood to come out when he drooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know when and where your father went to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No... he went to it by himself two or three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already know this is definitely suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably used this stepladder here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got on here and pulled the rope around the thick beam there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt this is suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his father was saying that he wanted to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:20:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told everybody at the station I was going to videotape Sleeping Kogoro's deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will I tell everyone when I get back to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a suicide, you don't have to bother with investigating further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man is bent over and only about 30 centimeters taller than me, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the string for the light here is made to fit the old man's height,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't reach it even if I stretch my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kid is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means this isn't a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, a while back when my father got up late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the string got in his face and he hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the light pull string in my father's room is short.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it is suicide after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be waiting downstairs in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so call me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting all of you dragged into something like this while on your vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you like fishing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This book, "Fishing for Beginners".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, my wife was the one bought that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife who passed away of illness 3 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I never saw her go fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so maybe she was planning on doing so after she recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something's strange about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:50.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The way he made Ran go all the way upstairs for the dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:53.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the length of the light's pull string,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:56.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the story about him going to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:22:00.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he knew that he got his teeth treated 2 or 3 days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}why did he make something like curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If when he was a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he made food and focused on nutrition,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he should have noticed that detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:14.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he made far too much for just the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:21.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He couldn't have known beforehand that we would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the knot tied on the pull string.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:28.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No question... {i dont think this is right but its what viz had}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case... has something fishy behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but when I went in front of the room the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the old man weeping "Uuugh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get the picture... of this trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.64,0:24:22.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay, now that I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:26.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:29.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I lost my voice!
